    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of every single detail, so it's sparkling clean and ready for its next adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and feels brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
