    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a known structural pain point\u2014has been reinforced with precision plates. The factory limited-slip differential operates flawlessly, and the suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers. Zero evidence of thermal cycling fatigue on the valve cover or fluid leaks. This is a turn-key chassis for the discerning collector who demands peak atmospheric performance and a documented service pedigree.",
      "price": 44900.0,
